I2C tool utility

Syntax:
  # i2c-tool -d [device name] -a [i2c dev address] -r/-w [reg address:hex] -c [write data:hex] -h

Options:
  device name: device node path. Ex: /dev/i2c2
  speed      : I2C bus speed 
  h          : help message
    
Launch examples:
# i2c-tool -d /dev/i2c2 -a 0x2c -r 0x0c
# i2c-tool -d /dev/i2c2 -a 0x2c -w 0x0c -c 0x80
# i2c-tool -h

